      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. it's a good start but it feels a little too generic. can u make it sound a bit more personal? maybe something that acknowledges the specific difficulty of the decision since they were such a strong contender, but keep it very formal so we don't give them false hope or anything. just a bit more warmth?",
